------------------------------- RELEASE 0.8 ------------------------------------

- dropX11Extras by using completeley only XCB
- Multithreading
- Use matchers - Only large indexes have search indexes (Files), [ needs profiler ]
- port to way more flexible qml - Check the QtQuick standard project
- final hotkey refinement (XCB) - multiple independant hotkeys, qxtglobalshortcut,
- Pluginmanager as treeview (Group, Extension, Subextension) - with QDataWidgetMapper
- python integration - special plugin interface, (Calc (Sympy), Terminal, ssh). Closes #13
- Plugin Interdependenciea - https://doc-snapshots.qt.io/qtcreator-extending/extensionsystem-pluginspec.html#details
- Make the indexing fingrained by mimetype
- Profiler - Extensionmanager profiles extensions (SQLITE backend), Dummy extension with 1M results
- [#8] QDesktopWidget * QApplication::desktop()
- [Actions][Modifier] Preset modifier to action map
- [Actions][Modifier] Configurable modifier to action map
- [Actions][Interdep.] - e.g. open files with app actions
- better scoring
- Port Hotkeymanager to xcb (http://xcb.freedesktop.org/) ask peole to start something like qxt-community

- Open on screen with mouse. Remember window position preference #33, #8
- Allow only one instance of Albert #23
- Please allow fuzzy matching of spaces to underscores #40



